	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heri, venerandissime d. pater, cuidam puero commisi literas d. <persName ref="p8432" cert="high">Friderici a Salicibus</persName> ad te perferendas; nunc autem, cum iuratum tabellionem ex urbe vestra acceperimus, non committam, quin literis etiam meis oneratus discedat, quibus et reditum nostrum, et quid in eo evenerit, brevibus depingam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dextre ad penates nostros pervenimus omniaque salva invenimus dei gratia.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ammanus autem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l108">Davosius</placeName>, antequam lacum <placeName type="auto_name">Rivanum</placeName> attingeremus, recta quorundam negociorum suorum causa ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l646" cert="high">Glaronenses</placeName> se contulit; nos soli lacum traiecimus.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Subsecutus postero die <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiam</placeName> pervenit mirifica narrans scommata, quibus <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Glaronae</placeName> a malevolis fuit ictus et exceptus: 'Quid nostra refert, quid <placeName type="citizen_name">Helvetii</placeName> reliqui constituerint?</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habemus in nostris manibus transitum peculiarem, cuius iure utemur porro, sicuti incępimus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ubi dominus <placeName type="auto_name">Rhetiensis</placeName>?</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si huc tecum venisset, vino nimirum honorario illum exciperemus scilicet etc.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec et alia eblaterarunt temere.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed haec omnia ammanus <persName type="auto_name">Fridolini</persName> sacris ascribit, quae tunc temporis celebrarunt temulenti; nam postero die rogatus fuit, ne quid aegre ferret; plus satis enim in festo potatum fuisse.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec d. consul secreto mecum communicavit exspectans accessionem aliquam, quam deinceps in socios querebundi exonerent.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Prae caeteris autem <persName type="citizen_name">Ludo[v]icus Tschudius</persName> acrem se praebuit.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid fiat in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName> inter proceres et quomodo <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2652" cert="high">Cyprum</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcicus</placeName> furor bello lacescere praesumpserit, procul dubio d. <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p8432">Fridericus</persName> ad te perscripsit.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De expeditione autem Rhetica nihildum audio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Aber zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name">Wesen</placeName> lag es als voll junger schnüderliggen; da was ouch das fendle und ein toubs geschrey.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott erbarms!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec ad te ocyus, colendissime d. pater, quibus subnectens vehementer oro rogoque, ut nos tuae fidei et humanitati nunquam non habeas commendatos.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas etiam puero dedi praedicto ad d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1012" cert="high">Ernium</persName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1012" cert="high">Leonhard Erni</persName>.</note>, amicorum optimo, quas certe curatas cupidissime velim.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant te d. consules, d. <persName type="auto_name">Carolus</persName>, qui ex te scire cupit, <foreign xml:lang="de">ob man ouch zuͦ <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName> doctores mache der beider rechten, geistlich und w[eltlich],</foreign> d. <persName ref="p6130" cert="high">Pontisella</persName>, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20473" cert="high">Gantnerus</persName> et nemo non bonus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curię</placeName> 14. martii 1570.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuae dominationi subiectissimus <persName ref="p8016" cert="high">Th[obias] Eg[lius</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amplissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Hennrico Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae antistiti primario, domino patri suo singulari observantia colendissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ann m. <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Heinrych Bullinger</persName> zuͦ <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
